<h1>Welcome to Photo App</h1>
<p>Email in Production</p>
<p> heroku addons:create sendgrid:starter</p>
<p>heroku config:set SENDGRID_USERNAME=</p>
<p>heroku config:set SENDGRID_PASSWORD=</p>
<p>open .zshrc</p>
<p>export SENDGRID_USERNAME=</p>
<p>export SENDGRID_PASSWORD=</p>
<h4>Now in enviorment.rb</h5>
<p>
  ActionMailer::Base.smtp_settings = {
  :address => 'smtp.sendgrid.net',
  :port => '587',
  :authentication => :plain,
  :user_name => ENV['SENDGRID_USERNAME'],
  :password => ENV['SENDGRID_PASSWORD'],
  :domain => 'heroku.com',
  :enable_starttls_auto => true
  }
</p>

<h4>Now in development.rb</h5>
<p>
  config.action_mailer.delivery_method = :test
</p>
<p>
  config.action_mailer.default_url_options = { :host => 'http://localhost:3000'}
</p>


<h4>Now in production.rb</h5>
<p>
  config.action_mailer.delivery_method = :smtp
</p>
<p>
  config.action_mailer.default_url_options = { :host => 'MyLiveSiteUrl.com', :protocol => 'https' }
</p>
